1
00:00:00,120 --> 00:00:02,080
So, this might be really hard to hear,

2
00:00:02,080 --> 00:00:03,310
but if you're spending money

3
00:00:03,310 --> 00:00:05,080
on more than one of these things,

4
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:06,710
you'll never become rich.

5
00:00:06,710 --> 00:00:09,160
Well, unless you have an
extremely high paid job

6
00:00:09,160 --> 00:00:10,330
or win the lottery.

7
00:00:10,330 --> 00:00:12,210
Now lots of people will try and tell you

8
00:00:12,210 --> 00:00:13,810
that becoming rich is easy.

9
00:00:13,810 --> 00:00:15,350
Probably because they want to sell you

10
00:00:15,350 --> 00:00:17,340
some sort of get-rich-quick scheme.

11
00:00:17,340 --> 00:00:19,290
However, this isn't the case,

12
00:00:19,290 --> 00:00:20,920
especially at a young age.

13
00:00:20,920 --> 00:00:23,130
It's not impossible to become wealthy,

14
00:00:23,130 --> 00:00:25,600
but you do have to be very strategic.

15
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:27,600
I'm not pretending to sell a magic bullet.

16
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:29,450
In fact, I'm not selling anything,

17
00:00:29,450 --> 00:00:32,100
I just enjoy sharing my
