258
00:09:08,260 --> 00:09:10,070
I guess I was ahead of my time.

259
00:09:10,070 --> 00:09:12,530
Lucky seven is passion purchases.

260
00:09:12,530 --> 00:09:14,287
I know I'm probably
gonna get comments like,

261
00:09:14,287 --> 00:09:16,840
"Mark, I'd rather enjoy
my life while I'm young,

262
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,330
then be rich when I'm old."

263
00:09:18,330 --> 00:09:19,840
I completely see your point.

264
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,360
However, you can save money

265
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:23,640
and still have a lot
of fun in the process.

266
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:25,810
It doesn't have to be one or the other.

267
00:09:25,810 --> 00:09:27,580
Everyone has a passion for something.

268
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:29,770
Mine is flying radio-controlled models.

269
00:09:29,770 --> 00:09:32,240
Back in the day, the
latest and best new models

270
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,500
always appeal to me.

271
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:36,760
And that's my shop sold these,
the temptation was huge.

272
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:40,100
They were always right in front
of me, begging to be flown.

273
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:42,810
Contrary to what everyone
thinks, the products aren't free,

274
00:09:42,810 --> 00:09:45,930
so taking models off the shelf
leads to a loss of profit.

275
00:09:45,930 --> 00:09:48,470
So I decided that I
would repair all models

276
00:09:48,470 --> 00:09:49,900
and fly these instead.

277
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:52,060
Sure, it's a bit more
work, but it was worth it

278
00:09:52,060 --> 00:09:53,280
as I still got to have fun,

279
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:55,360
but at a fraction of the price.

280
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,830
This way I've got some good models

281
00:09:56,830 --> 00:09:59,730
that I flew for a season and
then sold on for a profit

282
00:09:59,730 --> 00:10:02,000
to other people that
loved watching them fly.

283
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:04,330
I can afford to do any
hobby I want these days,

284
00:10:04,330 --> 00:10:06,150
but I still respect the value of money

285
00:10:06,150 --> 00:10:07,910
and refuse to overspend.

286
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:11,550
I think up to 5% of your
take-home pay is okay for a hobby.

287
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:13,360
Just remember whatever your passion,

288
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:16,290
if you can make it pay for
itself, then you're laughing.

289
00:10:16,290 --> 00:10:18,460
Number eight is untracked subscriptions.

290
00:10:18,460 --> 00:10:20,380
It's estimated that in this country,

291
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:24,303
people waste $34 billion
on unwanted subscriptions

292
00:10:24,303 --> 00:10:26,080
that they don't even use.

293
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,320
No wonder software companies

294
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:30,000
are all moving to a
subscription business model.

295
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,840
But I'll give it to them.

296
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:33,520
It's a great way to
get reoccurring revenue

297
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:35,750
without having to find a new customer.

298
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:38,440
They can just keep selling
to you again, and again,

299
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,860
and again, and again, and again.

300
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:40,730
Now let's be honest.

301
00:10:40,730 --> 00:10:42,700
Subscriptions can easily add up

302
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:44,740
and are also tricky to manage.

303
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:46,280
As I've mentioned previously,

304
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:48,870
there's a subscription
for everything nowadays.

305
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:52,090
You can even get toilet paper
on subscription from Amazon.

306
00:10:52,090 --> 00:10:54,130
Oh, Curtis, remember
to set that up for me.

307
00:10:54,130 --> 00:10:55,360
- [Curtis] I've got you dad, don't worry.

308
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:57,220
- But not all subscriptions are bad.

309
00:10:57,220 --> 00:10:58,610
When I was younger, every Friday,

310
00:10:58,610 --> 00:10:59,690
me and a bunch of mates

311
00:10:59,690 --> 00:11:01,750
would go to catch a movie at the cinema.

312
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:04,210
I have to be honest, it became a bad habit

313
00:11:04,210 --> 00:11:06,400
that was eating into my finances.

314
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:09,290
I mean, the popcorn, drinks, ticket costs,

315
00:11:09,290 --> 00:11:12,430
and toll charges really started adding up.

316
00:11:12,430 --> 00:11:15,130
If you will spend in a
day's income on a night out,

317
00:11:15,130 --> 00:11:17,160
you're caught in a never ending cycle.

318
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:18,140
To get around this,

319
00:11:18,140 --> 00:11:21,060
we decided to hire a
film from Blockbuster.

320
00:11:21,060 --> 00:11:22,240
You probably don't remember them,

321
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,900
but they were massive in the day.

322
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:25,650
And my mates would come around my house

323
00:11:25,650 --> 00:11:27,730
and supply the drinks and popcorn,

324
00:11:27,730 --> 00:11:29,580
therefore, splitting the cost

325
00:11:29,580 --> 00:11:31,340
and getting a better experience.

326
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:32,510
Because we didn't have to worry about

327
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:35,400
other people in the movie
theater, or the traveling.

328
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:37,960
So my point here is that
subscriptions like Netflix

329
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:40,200
can actually be a huge money saver,

330
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:43,340
as it allows you to have fun
at home for a very low cost.

331
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:46,040
But many subscriptions
could get out of control.

332
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:48,030
And when you're done using
them, the facts show,

333
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:51,690
you won't even cancel them,
which is absolutely bonkers.

334
00:11:51,690 --> 00:11:53,570
So as long as you're using the service

335
00:11:53,570 --> 00:11:54,670
and getting good value,

336
00:11:54,670 --> 00:11:56,910
then I don't think there's
too much of an issue here.

337
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:58,000
If you try hard enough,

338
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:01,240
you will always be able to find
creative ways to save money.

339
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:03,620
But this is also just
one side of the battle.

340
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:06,380
You of course also need to
be increasing your income

341
00:12:06,380 --> 00:12:07,640
at the same time.

342
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:10,340
I've made tons of other videos
about making more money.

343
00:12:10,340 --> 00:12:12,120
So I'm gonna leave the
next video right up there.

344
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,590
But don't click on it just yet!

345
00:12:13,590 --> 00:12:16,510
Make sure to subscribe if you
wanna grow your wealth, okay?

346
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:17,970
I'll see you over there.

